      <div class="form-group col-md-12">
        <li class="list-group-item">2. Leave $1000 for small emergency fund. Puts the rest into level 3. For rest of the level as soon as the stash reaches $2000 it will leave $1000 in the small emergency fund and take the rest and plugs into the level. </li>
