        <li class="list-group-item">3. Pay off credit card debts aggressively. (Smallest to largest)</li>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group col-md-12">
        <li class="list-group-item">4. Pay off other consumer debts (car payments, student loans, medical payments). (Smallest to largest)</li>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group col-md-12">
